.gov.br/os_deputados/conheca_os_deputados/perfil/91-francisco-accioly-rodrigues-da-costa-filho Perfil Accioly Filho] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141028085923/http://www.alep.pr.gov.br/os_deputados/conheca_os_deputados/perfil/91-francisco-accioly-rodrigues-da-costa-filho |date=2014-10-28 }} Assembl\u00e9ia Legislativa do Paran\u00e1 - ALEP {{in lang|pt}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== Bibliography ==\n* NICOLAS, Maria. 130 Anos de Vida Parlamentar Paranaense - Assembleias Legislativas e Constituintes. 1854\u20131954. 2\u00b0 ed. Curitiba: Assembl\u00e9ia Legislativa do Paran\u00e1; 1984. 779p\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Rodrigues, Francisco}}\n[[Category:Members of the Federal Senate]]\n[[Category:1920 births]]\n[[Category:1979 deaths]]\n[[Category:People from Paranagu\u00e1]]\n\n\n{{Brazil-politician-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Orphan|date=February 2015}}\n{{Infobox politician\n| name          = Accioly Filho\n| image         = Accioly Filho senador.jpg\n| alt           = \n| caption       = \n| candidate     = \n| election_date = \n| runningmate   = \n| opponent      = \n| incumbent     = \n| birth_date    = {{birth date|1920|3|5|df=yes}}\n| birth_place   = [[Paranagu\u00e1]], Brazil\n| death_date    = {{death date and age|1979|11|12|1920|3|5|df=yes}}\n| death_place   = [[Curitiba]], Brazil\n| party         = \n| otherparty    = \n| relations     = \n| spouse        = \n| civil partner = \n| children      = \n| residence     = \n| occupation    = \n| religion      = \n| signature     = \n| signature_alt = \n| website       = \n| footnotes     = \n}}\n'''Francisco Accioly Rodrigues da Costa Filho''' (5 March 1920 in [[Paranagu\u00e1]] &ndash; 13 November 1979 in [[Curitiba]]) was a [[Brazil]]ian lawyer, professor, and politician. He was a [[Brazilian Senate|Senator of the Republic]] between 1971 and 1978.<ref>[http://www.projetovip.net/0305.htm Nascimentos em 5 de Mar\u00e7o] Projeto VIP {{in lang|pt}}</ref><ref>[http://www.oexplorador.com.br/franc